 width=\"101\" valign=\"center\" style=\"width:76.0000pt;padding:0.0000pt 5.4000pt 0.0000pt 5.4000pt ;border-left:1.0000pt solid windowtext;\r\n      mso-border-left-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;border-right:1.0000pt solid windowtext;mso-border-right-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;\r\n      border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0000pt solid windowtext;\r\n      mso-border-bottom-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;\">\r\n      <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:26.0000pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1.24.</font><font face=\"宋体\">（初三）</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1.25.</font><font face=\"宋体\">（初四）</font></span></p>\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td width=\"119\" valign=\"center\" style=\"width:89.2500pt;padding:0.0000pt 5.4000pt 0.0000pt 5.4000pt ;border-left:1.0000pt solid windowtext;\r\n      mso-border-left-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;border-right:1.0000pt solid windowtext;mso-border-right-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;\r\n      border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0000pt solid windowtext;\r\n      mso-border-bottom-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext;\">\r\n      <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:26.0000pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">呼吸内科、</font></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">皮肤科、</font></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">消化内科、神经内科、心血管内科、骨科、普通外科、感染科、妇科、儿科（设在急诊）等</font></span></p>\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td width=\"119\" valign=\"center\" style=\"width:89.3500pt;padding:0.0000pt 5.4000pt 0.0000pt 5.4000pt ;border-left:1.0000pt solid windowtext;\r\n      mso-border-left-alt:0.5000pt solid windowtext