n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">△盐城市一院内科副主任、消化内科主任、主任医师王建华主持会议。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt;\'><span><img width=\"438\" height=\"328\" align=\"center\" src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2023/02/06/20230206155334646003.png\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">△吴东教授以《肺肠微生态轴对急性胰腺炎的诊疗意义》《</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">IBD</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">内镜诊断、评估和监测》为主题进行授课，对急性胰腺炎和</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">IBD</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">的诊治进行细致的分析和讲解。</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">\r\n</span>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">\r\n</span>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 21.1pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><br>\r\n</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 21.1pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">专家链接——</span></b></p>\r\n