pan style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">(1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">）法人或者其他组织的营业执照等证明文件，自然人的身份证明；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">(2)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">上一年度的财务报表（成立不满一年不需提供）；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">(3)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">依法缴纳税收和社会保障资金的相关材料；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">(4)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">具备履行合同所必需的设备和专业技术能力的书面声明；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">(5)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">参加政府采购活动前<span>3</span>年内在经营活动中没有重大违法记录的书面声明；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">本项目的特定资格要求：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">（<span>1</span>）未被“信用中国”网站（<span>www.creditchina.gov.cn</span>）列入失信被执行人、重大税收违法案件当事人名单、政府采购严重失信行为记录名单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:26.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">（<span>2</span>）单位负责人为同一人或者存在直接控股、管理关系的不同供应商，不得参加同一合同项下的政府采购活动。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:1.5\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">三、获取招标文件</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">时间</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间<span>2023</span>年<span>4</span>月<span>7</span>日<span>8</span>时<span>30</span>分至<span>2023</span>年<span>4</span>月<span>13</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">日<span>18</span>时。联系人：刘工，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm;line-height:1.5\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">四、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">本项目采用<span>“</span>经评审的最低投标价法<span>”</span>。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">五、投标人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，采购人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">六、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:1.5\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">七、对本次招标提出询问，请按以下方式联系。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">采购人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp;\r\n</span>址：人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">联系人：张女士</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">电<span>&nbsp;\r\n</span>话：<span>0515-66696855</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">招标代理机构：江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">地址：盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>805</span>室<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">联系人：刘工<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">电话：<span>0515-69057406&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('3052','3877','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院发电机组维保项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。1、项目概况与招标内容1.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院发电机组维保项目。1.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路66号）、北','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1680832832','<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\">盐城市第一人民医院发电机组维保项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span>1</span>、项目概况与招标内容</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span>1.1</span>项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院发电机组维保项目。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span>1.2</span>项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）、北区（毓龙西路<span>166</span>号）、五官科医院（南城河路<span>12</span>号）。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院发电机组维保项目包含但不限于：主院区发电机组<span>6</span>台（<span>4</span>台<span>1000KW</span>、<span>2</span>台<span>200KW</span>），北区发电机组<span>1</span>台<span>300KW</span>，五官科医院发电机组<span>1</span>台<span>150KW</span>。</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标人保留对上述招标范围进行适当调整的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">维保期限：<span>2</span>年。具体维保开始日期以书面合同签订日期为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">最高限价：<span>12.3</span>万元</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span>2</span>、投标人资格要求</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span>2.1</span>投标人应具有独立法人资格，能够独立承担民事责任的能力。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span>2.2</span>项目负责人为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2023</span>年<span>2</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2022</span>年<span>7</span>月<span>-2023</span>年<span>1</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）（投标时提供社保证明材料）。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">其他要求<span><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.3.1</span>财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp; 2.3.2</span>信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span>3</span>、投标报名及招标文件的获取</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span style=\"background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间<span>2023</span>年<span>4</span>月<span>7</span>日<span>8</span>时<span>30</span>分至<span>2023</span>年<span>4</span>月<span>13</span>日<span>18 </span>时。联系人：刘工，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span>4</span>、<b>评标办法<span>:</span>采用“经评审的最低投标价法”。</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span>5</span>、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:27.0pt\"><span>6</span>、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\">地址：盐城市人民南路<span>66</span>号</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\">联系人：张女士</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\">联系电话：<span>0515-66696855 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\">招标代理机构：江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司 </p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\">地址：盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>805</span>室<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\">联系人：刘工<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\">电话：<span>0515-69057406&nbsp; </span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('3053','3878','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院净化空调初、中效过滤器采购项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。1、项目概况 1.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院净化空调初、中效过滤器采购项目。1.2服务地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区、','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1680832885','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院净化空调初、中效过滤器采购项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、项目概况<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院净化空调初、中效过滤器采购项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">服务地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区、北院区、五官科医院。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院净化空调初、中效过滤器采购项目，具体详见项目需求。北区（毓龙西路<span>166</span>号）及五官科医院（南城河路<span>12</span>号）空气过滤器由中标人负责安装，主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）空气过滤器由医院自行安装。上述费用请投标人报价时综合考虑，结算时招标人不另行增加费用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量标准：满足国家合格标准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">工期：<span>15</span>个日历天。具体开始日期以招标人的通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">最高限价：<span>25</span>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、 投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人应具有独立法人资格，能够独立承担民事责任的能力。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目负责人为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2023</span>年<span>2</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2022</span>年<span>7</span>月<span>-2023</span>年<span>1</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）（投标时提供社保证明材料）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">其他要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">号</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">楼</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">805</span><span style=\"background:white\">室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">2023</span><span style=\"background:\r\nwhite\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">7</span><span style=\"background:white\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">时</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">30</span><span style=\"background:white\">分至</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">2023</span><span style=\"background:white\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">4</span><span style=\"background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">13</span><span style=\"background:white\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">18</span><span style=\"background:white\">时。联系人：刘工，</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">0515-69057406</span><span style=\"background:white\">；手机：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">13626222271</span><span style=\"background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"background:white\">、<b>评标办法</b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">:</span></b><b><span style=\"background:\r\nwhite\">采用“经评审的最低投标价法”。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"background:white\">、投标人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"background:white\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室，联系电话</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">0515-66696810</span><span style=\"background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地址：盐城市人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-6.0pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联系人：张女士</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.