gn:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地址：盐城市青年路钱江财富广场西区</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">楼</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联系人：吴女士</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:21.0pt;\r\nline-height:23.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电话：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">0515-89803566</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">15950298580</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('3068','3893','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院雨污混接点改造项目资金已落实，我院现拟对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标，择优选择施工队伍。1、工程概况 1.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院雨污混接点改造项目1.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路66号）1.3招标内容：','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1683275542','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院雨污混接点改造项目资金已落实，我院现拟对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标，择优选择施工队伍。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程概况<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院雨污混接点改造项目</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目地点：<span style=\"color:blue\">盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院雨污混接点改造项目包含但不限于：新建隔油池，混凝土地面恢复，管道、井壁开洞封堵，砖井检查，门诊楼管道改造项目等内容，</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:blue\">具体内容详见招标人提供的工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准，符合环保、城镇排水管理处等部门要求，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">工期要求：<span>15</span>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的通知。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">最高限价：<span>&nbsp; 13 </span>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">2 </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人须具有建设行政主管部门核发的</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">市政公用工程施工总承包三级及以上资质</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">的独立法人，并取得有效的安全生产许可证。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目负责人的资格要求：项目负责人须具有市政公用工程专业二级及以上建造师注册证书；同时具有《建筑施工企业项目负责人安全生产考核合格证》（<span>B</span>类）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">其他要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0p